      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "This is more of a computer lab than a traditional classroom, with rows
    of desktop PCs set up across long benches and a projector screen at the front
    for when the whole group needs to focus on the same thing. \nThe teal walls give
    it a bit more character than your average teaching room, and the blinds mean
    glare on screens isn't a problem when you need them down. \nIt's a practical,
    no fuss space that's set up to get work done, the kind of room where you'll spend
    a good chunk of time depending on your course, and it doesn't take long to feel
    at home in it."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fa8262f62f0c58549807ecdb3cd379d0, type: 2}
